content: Blower Motor may Short Circuit and Cause Fire

Autocar, LLC (Autocar) is recalling certain 2020-2026 DC (Legend) vehicles.  The incorrect blower motor fuse may have been installed.An incorrect fuse may fail to trip, allowing the blower to short circuit and increasing the risk of a fire.

Number of Units Affected: 1000.0
